宾语：with flour sacks  用面粉袋
*/</span>
<span class="token class-name">The</span> sail was patched <span class="token keyword">with</span> <span class="token namespace">flour</span> sacks and<span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token comment">// 船帆用面粉袋打了些补丁</span>

furled<span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token comment">// 卷着的</span>

<span class="token doc-comment comment">/**
